Applications of iot:

1) Smart Retail                  :    Smart Product management
                                                    Layout optimization

2) Smart Factories           : Enterprise Asset management
                                                  Energy management

3) Water Management     : Water quality management
                                                    Monitoring water level

4) Smart Homes                :  Remote control applicance like fanswitch

5) Digital Health                :   Ultraviolet Radiation Monitoring
                                                  Fall detection

6) Smart Farming           :  Monitoring soil nutrients
                                                   Predictive rainfall
                                                   Different watering methods

7) Smart cities                 : Waste management
                                                 Outdoor survelliance
                                                 Noise monitoring

8) Smart Logistics         : Fleet tracking
                                            Connected vehicles

9) Smart Metering        : Smart grid

10)Smart Parking         : Vehicles management

11)Wearables            : Monitoring heartbeat 
                                      Detects glucose level in body

12)ForestFire Detection : Predict forestfire

13)Smart Lighting       : For energy efficiency

14)Mimo Monitors        : Monitoring baby's breathing,body temperature activity level

15)Ingestible Sensors   : Monitoring whether the patient taking   prescribed medications or not

16)Smart Toothbrush     : Teeth management

17)Smart refrigerator   : Monitor spoiled food
                                               Track leftover food

18)Pollution Warnings   : Detect pollutants emitted from vehicles

19)Self-Driving vehicles: Enable vehicle to sense the traffic,potholes

20)Ultraviolet Radiation: monitoring harmful rays

                        
                        
